Table Distortion by Daniel Gallardo
daniel.gallardo@upf.edu
MTG - Universitat Pompeu Fabra
Barcelona, Spain.

INSTALL
----------------------------------------------------------------------
*Place ofxTableDistortion folder into openframeworks addons directory
*Run command 'ofProject add YOUR_OF_PRJECT ofxTableDistortion'

Start
----------------------------------------------------------------------
*Create a TestApp class that inherits from TableApp.hpp
*Overwrite the following methods:
	-void Setup();
	-void Update();
	-void Draw();
	-void WindowResized(int w, int h);

Using it
----------------------------------------------------------------------
to show help content press 'h' at the app window

